---
By: Shantidasa
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 78
    Verse: 17
Tags:
  - Death
---
Do not allow death to disturb you, do not let the demise of flesh be the cause
of pain or anguish. It is merely rid dance of your vehicle, the sloughing
off of your clothes.
